included.description: To help parents organize kids' activities and motivate kids appropriately, continually and consistently we created an product called Treasure Trip. We made paper prototype and a working physical product using Arduino and other electronics. In the end we made a video to pitch our idea.

included.description: In this project, we use restaurant reviews from Yelp, to assist restaurant owners and managers make meaningful inferences about their business and customer satisfaction. We explore three key dimensions of the restaurant business, namely product, delivery and environment. Through text processing and sentiment analysis of reviews, we build an interactive dashboard to visualize food quality, service and physical environment.
